Appropriate levels of vitamin D must be upheld in the body in order to maintain calcium and phosphorus levels in a healthy physiologic range to sustain a variety of metabolic functions, transcription regulation, and bone metabolism [A223, L5689, L1782, L5771, F4027, F4042, F4048]. However, studies are also ongoing to determine whether or not cholecalciferol may also play certain roles in cancer, autoimmune disorders, cardiovascular disease, and other medical conditions that may be associated with vitamin D deficiency [L5689].','["M05BB09", "M05BX53", "M05BB07", "M05BB08", "A11CC55", "M05BB05", "A11CC05", "M05BB03", "M05BB04"]','[]'),(1556,'Biomox 500mg 12 cap','بيوموكس 500مجم 12 كبسولة','20','15','Antibiotic','Amoxicillin','Sedico','Cap','كبسولة','500mg','2','مضاد حيوي','','6221042162042','',3138,'2024-11-08',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Amoxicillin, or BRL-2333, is a penicillin G derivative first described in the literature in 1972.[A190648] Amoxicillin has similar activity to [penicillin] and [ampicillin], but leads to higher serum concentrations than ampicillin.[A190648]

