egative inotropic effect. dose: adult: po- angina pectoris; htn- 50-100 mg once daily. migraine prophylaxis 50-100 mg/day. indi','6221508010818','',1636,'2022-12-03',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Atenolol is a cardioselective beta-blocker used in a variety of cardiovascular conditions. 

